	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />does anyone here know how to make thier own cart labels?  i got a bunch off the internet, but i was wondering how they were done so nicely with the seal of quality and the manufacturer name.  i have photoshop, so i guess i just need the graphics.  any other tips would be greatly appreciated.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
